headline: Jack Henry Announces 2025 Cobalt Award Winners
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) is proud to announce the winners of the 2025 Cobalt Awards – six financial institutions and fintechs that are redefining what it means to serve their communities through innovation, integration, and education.
